## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **omaveloxolone Skyclarys 2023** = first FDA Friedreich ataxia therapy, 16+ years. Nrf2 activator (Keap1-Nrf2-ARE pathway) — MOXIe trial + open-label extension. mFARS slope reduction. paradigm shift: Friedreich = first hereditary ataxia 에 mechanistic disease-modifier. quantum-VQE 의 Nrf2/Keap1 PPI 가 fit.
2. **nomlabofusp (Larimar) frataxin protein replacement Phase 2** = direct frataxin replenishment. CPP-frataxin fusion subcutaneous. proof-of-concept frataxin level rescue. Phase 2 dose-finding 2024-2025.
3. **vatiquinone (PTC) Phase 3 MOVE-FA** = mitochondrial 15-LO / electron transport. EPI-743 family. 24-month pediatric Friedreich. 결과 mixed — primary endpoint missed but signal subgroup.
4. **chenodiol (chenodeoxycholic acid) 만성 CTX 표준** = CYP27A1 deficiency + bile acid replacement. Chenodal/Yenodali — orphan reissue. lifetime treatment 만성. early diagnosis = neurologic prevention.
5. **elamipretide (Stealth Bio)** = cardiolipin-targeted tetrapeptide. mitochondrial inner membrane. 만성 mitochondrial 다발 적응증 + Friedreich research. cross-mitochondrial.
6. **idebenone (Catena) EU 2008 Friedreich + LHON** = coenzyme Q10 analog. EU approved 2008 Friedreich (US 미승인). LHON sensory cross. quantum-VQE 의 mitochondrial complex I/III.
7. **troriluzole (BHV-4157) Phase 3 MODUL-AT** = riluzole prodrug glutamate modulator. BioHaven SCA Phase 3 — 결과 mixed primary missed but subset. 만성 SCA off-label riluzole 의 prodrug 형태.
8. **AAV gene therapy LX2006 + LX2020 (Lexeo)** = frataxin AAV CNS+cardiac dual tropism. Friedreich cardiomyopathy 사망 원인. 만성 Friedreich gene therapy paradigm. cross-gene_therapy_platform.
9. **ATXN3 + ATXN1 allele-specific ASO research** = SCA3/Machado-Joseph + SCA1 polyQ disease. tominersen (HD) failure 후 polyQ ASO 전략 재고. SCA-selective allele-specific safer than tominersen.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, hereditary ataxia 임상 의미 한정. omaveloxolone 2023 외 만성 small molecule 부재.

